# ── Swarm Foundry — distributable template ──
# Track the ENGINE (.claude/**, CLAUDE.md, README.md, wiki/, the *.template.md
# scaffolds, and the blank STATUS.md board). Ignore everything a research RUN
# generates so each user starts clean and produces their own case.

# ── Per-run research outputs (docs/business-model) ────────────────
# The filled-in venture context + live progress board
# (keep only the *.template.md scaffolds)
docs/business-model/00-CONTEXT.md
docs/business-model/STATUS.md

# Builder deliverables + red-team critiques (ws1.md … ws11.md, *.challenge.md)
docs/business-model/ws*.md
docs/business-model/*.challenge.md

# Measured token ledgers + run documentation (written by hooks)
docs/business-model/TOKENS.md
docs/business-model/TOKENS.jsonl
docs/business-model/TOKENS-SUMMARY.md
docs/business-model/RUN-LOG.md

# Capstone publication outputs
docs/business-model/WHITE-PAPER.md
docs/business-model/SUBSTACK-POST.md

# ── Local / personal Claude Code config (never distribute) ────────
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/*.local.json
.claude/.credentials.json

# ── Tool caches (GitNexus / Serena) — local-only index state ──────
.gitnexus/
.serena/

# ── OS / editor / runtime noise ───────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
*.log
node_modules/
